it's all gonna set in.

04:37.999 --> 04:42.999
It's amazing
what one text can do.

04:42.999 --> 04:43.999
Is everything
going okay outside?

04:43.999 --> 04:47.999
- Yeah.
- How're you feeling with me?

04:47.999 --> 04:50.999
Um, it's too early to tell.

04:50.999 --> 04:52.999
