of the evening.

11:28.999 --> 11:29.999
- All right.
- Day, whatever.

11:29.999 --> 11:31.999
- Okay, see you in there.
- Thank you. Lunch was great.

11:31.999 --> 11:32.999
- Lunch was great.
- Not a problem.

