to go back to the yacht.

12:03.999 --> 12:04.999
Okay. Perfect.
We'll radio them.

12:04.999 --> 12:06.999
They'll send a tender,
and we can ride on out.

12:06.999 --> 12:07.999
Yeah, let's do it.
Great.

12:07.999 --> 12:10.999
[upbeat music]

12:10.999 --> 12:12.999
♪ ♪

12:12.999 --> 12:14.999
- How was it?
- Did you have fun?

12:14.999 --> 12:16.999
- Great.
